---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About — TagSmith"
	description="TagSmith is a free, browser-based gamer tag generator. Learn how it works and why it's free."
	canonicalPath="/about"
>
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
		<h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#2B2013]">
			About TagSmith
		</h1>
		<div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-[#5C4F3D]">
			<p>
				TagSmith is a single-purpose tool for generating gamer tags,
				usernames, and Discord handles — entirely inside your web browser.
				Every tag is assembled on your device from hardcoded, curated word
				lists. Nothing you generate is ever uploaded to a server.
			</p>
			<p>
				Because there is no server-side processing, TagSmith can stay
				completely free with no account, no watermark, and no rate limits.
				The site is supported by on-page advertising.
			</p>
			<p>
				Pick a vibe — Fantasy, Sci-Fi, Edgy, or Cute — toggle numbers and
				the classic <strong class="text-[#2B2013]">xX&hellip;Xx</strong>
				decoration on or off, and click Generate as many times as you like.
				Your last ten tags stay visible so you can compare and copy the
				one you like best.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
